Release notes:
Minor feature polish.
* `ProcessPromise` and `ProcessOutput` `lines()` getters now accept a custom delimiter [#1220](https://github.com/google/zx/issues/1220) [#1218](https://github.com/google/zx/issues/1218)
```ts
const cwd = tempdir()
const delimiter = '\0'
const p1 = $({
cwd
})`touch foo bar baz; find ./ -type f -print0 -maxdepth 1`
(await p1.lines(delimiter)).sort() // ['./bar', './baz', './foo']
// or via options
const lines = []
const p2 = $({
delimiter,
cwd,
})`find ./ -type f -print0 -maxdepth 1`
for await (const line of p2) {
lines.push(line)
}
lines.sort() // ['./bar', './baz', './foo']
```
* Handle `.nothrow()` option in `ProcessProcess[AsyncIterator]` [#1216](https://github.com/google/zx/pull/1216) [#1217](https://github.com/google/zx/pull/1217)
* Updates yaml to [v2.8.0](https://github.com/eemeli/yaml/releases/tag/v2.8.0) [#1221](https://github.com/google/zx/pull/1221)
